ğŸƒ CARD #1: THE GREAT MILENKO (The Ringmaster)

"Here we go, here we go, here we go / Psychopathic Records in the place, you know"

What it controls: The Quest System - how your world creates goals and tasks

Your Dials:

Dial What it does Turn it UP (7+) Turn it DOWN (1-3)
Quest Frequency How often new quests appear Constant adventures, never bored Rare events, peaceful existence
Quest Complexity How complicated quests are Multi-stage epics with puzzles Simple "go here, do that" tasks
Reward Size What you get for finishing Legendary treasures, huge XP Small tokens, modest growth
Failure Consequences What happens if you quit Permanent changes, world shifts Try again, no big deal

How to adjust:

```python
# In your engine config
quest_config = {
    'frequency': 0.7,        # 0.0-1.0: How often new quests appear
    'complexity': 0.5,       # 0.0-1.0: How complicated quests are
    'reward_multiplier': 1.2, # 0.5-3.0: How good the rewards are
    'failure_penalty': 0.3,   # 0.0-1.0: How bad failure hurts
}
```

